    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TANKS Total Destruction</strong> 向经典致敬，并将其带入现代动作游戏的世界。固定的俯视视角（玩家可看到完整地图）、仅限四个方向的移动方式，以及紧张刺激的战术玩法，与现代画面、震撼的爆炸效果和由 Unreal Engine 5 驱动的流畅动画完美结合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接高速坦克战斗吧——反应、配合与战术将决定胜负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含 <strong>25 张多样化地图</strong>，分布在不同环境中。每个战场都拥有独特的布局和挑战，让战斗始终充满新鲜感。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人模式</strong> —— 独自对抗一波又一波的敌人<br><strong>合作模式</strong> —— 与另一名玩家并肩作战，释放毁灭力量（两名玩家可共用一个键盘）<br><strong>本地多人模式（最多 4 人）</strong> —— 单屏激烈战斗，非常适合沙发同乐</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏规则</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>TANKS Total Destruction</strong> 中，你操控的坦克只能向四个方向移动，并始终朝当前朝向射击。地图中唯一的障碍物是建筑和水域：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每栋建筑可被三次射击摧毁</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/80cec82410b8192214fdb154b27e15b6.poster.avif?t=1770500405\" width=1170 height=630 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/80cec82410b8192214fdb154b27e15b6.webm?t=1770500405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/80cec82410b8192214fdb154b27e15b6.mp4?t=1770500405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水域无法穿越，但可以射击穿过</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/5418d2076e2da4f409f1c424df52e55d.poster.avif?t=1770500405\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/5418d2076e2da4f409f1c424df52e55d.webm?t=1770500405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/5418d2076e2da4f409f1c424df52e55d.mp4?t=1770500405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图上没有其他障碍物</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/605fe379fe3d852e31aaafd9d7849dde.poster.avif?t=1770500405\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/605fe379fe3d852e31aaafd9d7849dde.webm?t=1770500405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/605fe379fe3d852e31aaafd9d7849dde.mp4?t=1770500405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌方坦克共有三种类型：普通型、快速型和重型。重型坦克移动较慢，但可以承受两次命中。要生存并击败敌人，战术、反应速度和地图意识至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连击系统至关重要——快速连续消灭多个敌人可获得分数加成，并带来最爽快的游戏时刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战场中散布着各种强化道具，用于升级你的坦克。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借多样的强化升级和独特的地图设计，每一场战斗都需要全新的策略和快速决策，完美融合经典机制与现代设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏将于 <strong>2026 年第一季度以抢先体验形式推出</strong>，并将按照下方路线图持续开发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>立即加入愿望单。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras/14a565dd7bc29f694d83e45125642e56.avif?t=1770500405\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4309500/extras_big/14a565dd7bc29f694d83e45125642e56.webp?t=1770500405 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
